//TUTORIALS This is the main screen Here you can find all the books in your collection, in 3 sections: Reading, Pending and Read This is the search screen Here you can search for new books to add to your collection This is the statistics screen Here you can see different statistics about all the books you have already read This is the settings screen Here you can modify your personal data and the app configuration This is the search bar Here you can search by the title for any book in your collection This is the synchronization button Here you can synchronize your data with the server, in case you have made any modification in another device This is the sort button Here you can sort the books in your collection by different values This is the search button Here you can search for the new books you want to add to your collection This is the save button Here you can save your personal data and the current app configuration after you modify it This is the delete profile button Here you can delete your profile and all the data you have created (user, password and books) This is the logout button Here you can logout, in case you want to login with a different user This is the add book button Here you can add this book to your collection This is the add image button Here you can add or change the book image. To do so, you must introduce the image link (http://…) that you should look for beforehand This is the rate book element Here you can rate this book from 1 to 10 (each star represents 2 points) This is the edit book button Here you can edit this book data This is the delete book button Here you can delete this book from your collection
